  "text": "With the equivalent elastic module E = 110.3 GPa [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] , the tip radius R = 300 nm and normal load F n = 3 to 67 μN, the contact pressure P c for the fabrication of protrusive nanostructures on quartz is calculated to be 4.3 to 12.1 GPa.",
